machine_end_gcode:
G91                   ; Relative positioning
G1 E-2 F2700          ; Retract a bit
G1 E-2 Z0.2 F2400     ; Retract more and raise Z
G1 X5 Y5 F3000        ; Wipe out

; Absolute positioning, move print head up
G90
G1{if max_layer_z < max_print_height} Z{z_offset+min(max_layer_z+30, max_print_height)}{endif} F720

G1 X0 Y210     ; Present print
M106 S0        ; Turn-off fan
M104 S0        ; Turn-off hotend
M140 S0        ; Turn-off bed
M84 X Y E      ; Disable all steppers but Z
machine_start_gcode:
M204 S[machine_max_acceleration_extruding] T[machine_max_acceleration_retracting]

G91                ; Relative positioning
G1 Z3.0 X3.0       ; Move X/Z away from end-stop
G1 Z10.0 F1500     ; Move Z axis up for probe
G90                ; Use absolute coordinates
M83                ; Extruder relative mode

M140 S[first_layer_bed_temperature]   ; Set bed temp
M280 P0 S160                          ; BLTouch alarm release
G4 P100                               ; Delay for BLTouch
G28                                   ; Home all
M190 S[first_layer_bed_temperature]   ; Wait for bed temp
M104 S180                             ; Set extruder stand-by temp
G29                                   ; Auto bed leveling
G1 Z5 X0 Y0 F3000                     ; Home for warm-up
M109 S[first_layer_temperature]       ; Wait for extruder temp

M300 P10               ; Beep beep, time to print
G92 E0                 ; Reset Extruder
G1 Z2.0 F1500          ; Move Z Axis up
G1 X10 Y5.0 Z0.5       ; Move to start position
G1 E4 F1200            ; Advance extruder
G1 Z0.3                ; Lower nozzle
G1 X130 E20            ; Draw the first line
G1 Y5.6                ; Step Y
G1 X70 E10             ; Draw the second (half) line
G1 E-0.1 F3600         ; Retract
G1 X80 Y5.3            ; Wipe right & down
G1 X90 Z0.5            ; Wipe right, lift nozzle
G92 E0                 ; Reset Extruder
name: MSDD E3 0.6 nozzle
